{"product_id":"oak-shampoo-imperial-for-men","title":"Magrada Oak Shampoo For Men 250ml","description":"\u003cdiv class=\"entry-content\"\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eA modern approach to the world of men – primal and earthy components create a shampoo with a light, modern and delicate nature! A natural shampoo for everyday use. The shampoo with a fine lather and minimal composition contains a powerful oak root extract that soothes irritated scalp and stimulates hair growth.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eDandelion extract\u003c\/span\u003e has anti-inflammatory and anti-irritation effect on the skin.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eOak root extract\u003c\/span\u003e has natural antimicrobial properties, soothing irritated and swollen skin.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe fragrance is derived from the blossoms of the evergreen shrub \u003cem\u003eOsmanthus\u003c\/em\u003e, the aroma is fresh and exquisite. The bush is also known as devilwood, because its smell is nothing less than tempting. Soft, woody, sensual, milky and leathery notes emerge from the fragrance notes.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use: \u003c\/strong\u003eApply the shampoo thoroughly on wet hair. Massage into a lather. Rinse. Repeat the procedure, if necessary.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eStore at a temperature of 5 – 25 degrees. Protect from direct sunlight during storage. Do not store the product near heaters or other heat sources.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e Aqua, Sodium Lauroyl Methyl Isethionate, Cocamidopropyl Betaine, Sodium Methyl Oleoyl Taurate, Lauryl Glucoside, Coco-Glucoside, Parfum, Quercus Robur (Oak) Bark Extract, Citric Acid, Taraxacum Officinale (Dandelion) Extract, Panthenol, Pentylene Glycol, Phenylpropanol, Sodium Benzoate\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eIngredients of natural origin: 94,88%.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe list of ingredients may be changed. Please see the packaging for the updated and most accurate list of ingredients.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eparaben-free \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e sulphate-free \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e silicone-free \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e vegan \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e alcohol-free | EU allergen-free | cruelty-free \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e hand-made \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e with a minimal list of ingredients\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e","brand":"Magrada Organic Cosmetics","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":48927684231495,"sku":"","price":13.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/magrada-oak-shampoo-for-men-250ml-302851.png?v=1739897400","url":"https:\/\/bioskina.com\/products\/oak-shampoo-imperial-for-men","provider":"bioskina","version":"1.0","type":"link"}